rows.label: qst650403_msg0001
rows.name: Heads up. Ignas, at twelve o'clock.

rows.label: qst650403_msg0002
rows.name:
Look like Nascion and others
are with them also.

rows.label: qst650403_msg0003
rows.name:
They don't look like any tribe I've
ever seen...

rows.label: qst650403_msg0004
rows.name:
Could they have banded together
to organize their actions...?

rows.label: qst650403_msg0007
rows.name:
If an Igna with potential touches a
Core Crystal, a Blade will be awakened.
It's not unheard of.

rows.label: qst650403_msg0008
rows.name: What it is, though, is a bloody nuisance.

rows.label: qst650403_msg0009
rows.name:
Nascion and the others are
in major danger...

rows.label: qst650403_msg0011
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Let those children go, you jerkfaces!!!

rows.label: qst650403_msg0013
rows.name:
That Igna surprisingly good at
giving direction... Tone was firm,
yet commanding...

rows.label: qst650403_msg0014
rows.name:
We should be giving them a beating,
not an ego boost!

rows.label: qst650403_msg0015
rows.name: Come on, let's back Hibana up!

rows.label: qst650403_msg0016
rows.name:
Sorry, guys...
It looks like I spooked them...

rows.label: qst650403_msg0017
rows.name:
Don't worry about that now, Hibana.
It's time to kick some lizard tail.

rows.label: qst650403_msg0018
rows.name:
Indeed. There will be time enough
for introspection later.
